______________________________________

Made by Paper-Cut. 
______________________________________

After being fed up with the low quality hosties maps that were flooding the hosties servers, I took it upon myself to make a hosties map that was not only balanced in terms of gameplay, but also visually appealing. The map's theme is loosely based on de_nuke, and is basically a hybrid between ultra-realism and unbelievability. The map contains 2 (large) jail cells, a wall, a gun pit, t spawn (complete with rebel way), gun toss, a pit for chicken fight/knife fight/western shootout, and a shot for shot arena. Also included with the map is a radar overlay. Note: The radar has a small bug where it stretches once outside of the boundaries of the map (you'll see what I mean). From what I could tell, it's nothing to worry about.
______________________________________

Install: Put the bsp into cstrike/maps folder.
______________________________________

Thanks goes out to:

Ryan Sterner, for help with optimization.
TAG Servers, for hosting both betas and providing various feedback from the playerbase
Etrigan, for ideas and testing along the way.
Turkey Eater, for ideas and testing along the way.

Property of Me(K.InC)

Since hosties is become a more well-known way to play CSS I decided to make a map depicting the elements of a good hosties game. Hosties is a game where the Ts are the "hosteges" and must do as the CTs say. Ts are suppposed to drop their weapon at the beginning of the round but may choose to smuggle the pistol. While following CT instructions, such as entering the jail, Ts must look for a chance to stab the CTs in the back(or wherever) and steal their weapon, then kill the other CTs, lead the rebellion for freedom!!!!! Ts could also look for a chance to breakaway from the group and find a place to hide, where if they have a pistol they may want to try to pick CTs off with it. Hosties is a very fun game and should really be taken into consideration.

Features:
A working Jailcell with working button controlled door
A Sniper Perchch to watch all those sneaky Ts
A Metal 4 Story Building
A pain chamber to send those Ts
Remote controlled Turret curtosey of Jonny-higgins 
4 SECRETS!!!! Including control to the auto turret
3 different pistol spawns in T spawn(only allowed to smuggle pistols anyway)
A little better decal use
Trucks to place the Ts in, divide and conqure style
A second, underground floor for the Ts to make a break for

If your going to give me negative feedback because you cant play a normal game on this remember:
Its not ment to play a normal CTs vs Ts its ment entirely to play Hosties!!!!

Any Feedback is greatly appreciated and this is my first map so be nice :D

This hosties map is based in a park-like area with a subway area located beneath the main playing field. The CT's start above ground who must prepare for and escort the T's from the prison transport. The T's can either exit once the transport via a main door opened by the CT's or take a secondary route that leads underneath the train cart into a vent onto the other side of the subway inaccessible by the CT's. From there, the T's can hold up or teleport to the rebel house for some good old fashion gunfighting. This map has all the requirements to play the hosties game type.

- Arena for chicken and knife fights
- Shot for shot platforms located just in front of CT spawn
- 1-way wall for Simon Says and other games
- Gun Toss wedge located next to 1-way wall
- 4 jail cells with windowed roofs

*This map has no secrets or Easter Eggs

This map sponsored by intox. Gaming, visit us at www.intoxGaming.com

Enjoy!
